    • import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { Bird } from 'src/app/model/bird.model'; import { BirdService } from 'src/app/services/bird.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-bird', templateUrl: './bird.component.html', styleUrls: ['./bird.component.scss'], }) export class BirdComponent implements OnInit { public list: any; public birds: Bird[] = []; constructor(private birdService: BirdService) {} ngOnInit(): void { this.getBird; } public getBird() { debugger; this.list = this.birdService .getBirds() .subscribe((item: any) => console.log((this.birds = item))); } }
